{"tid":1950124,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉貼笑話] 眾神仙在天庭聚集開例會...","createTime":"2020-03-30T06:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T15:11:30.000Z","uid":45772,"like":63,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f23143d98914cfed59be8876593192064ab222","tid":1950124,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:25:26.000Z","msg":"眾神仙在天庭聚集開例會...<br />\n<br />\n玉皇大帝問： 很久沒有見千手觀音， 有沒有他消息？<br />\n回答：他仍未洗完手啊...<br />\n<br />\n玉帝再問： 四面佛在哪？<br />\n答： 他不夠口罩啊<br />\n<br />\n玉帝又問：二郎神那裏去？<br />\n答： 他找不到第三隻眼的保護鏡呀...<br />\n<br />\n玉帝甚為不悅，說： 還有誰未到？<br />\n答： 關公面紅疑似發燒， 自我隔離中... 唐三藏取西經後未能入境...<br />\n<br />\n玉帝問：點解何仙姑，鉄拐李果幾條友都冇浦頭呢?<br />\n<br />\n答： 八仙多過4個人聚集俾人拉左😇<br />\n<br />\n最後玉帝無可奈何宣布休會至少十四天至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n玉帝最後問：閻羅王嗰邊情況係點。<br />\n眾神仙答：只有佢，仍然未封關😂😂"},{"pid":"4cf9675328e878cd7bffb3746e3156a556c4514d","tid":1950124,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:27:18.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4156918cb74f6d2e5e8bdfede0a1924011f26f","tid":1950124,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />dllm"},{"pid":"890edab980c761db2488c644b5f372e72ff4f9ef","tid":1950124,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:32:54.000Z","msg":"funny"},{"pid":"85c583f57e940dd6a6bd3ab64739d4396add6d3a","tid":1950124,"uid":235814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" c